# Build stage
FROM maven:3.9.6-eclipse-temurin-21 AS builder

LABEL stage=builder

WORKDIR /build

COPY pom.xml .
COPY src ./src

RUN mvn clean package -DskipTests

# Runtime stage
FROM eclipse-temurin:21-jre-alpine

LABEL maintainer="team@example.com" \
      app="analytics-dashboard" \
      version="1.0.0"

RUN apk add --no-cache curl fontconfig ttf-dejavu ca-certificates openssl && \
    rm -rf /var/cache/apk/*

WORKDIR /app

COPY --from=builder /build/target/*.jar ./app.jar

RUN apk add --no-cache openjdk17-jre && \
    aws_root_ca_url="https://truststore.pki.rds.amazonaws.com/global/global-bundle.pem" && \
    curl -sSL "$aws_root_ca_url" -o /tmp/rds-ca.pem && \
    keytool -import -alias rds-ca -file /tmp/rds-ca.pem \
        -keystore /usr/lib/jvm/java-17-openjdk/lib/security/cacerts \
        -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/rds-ca.pem && \
    azure_cert_url="https://cacerts.digicert.com/DigiCertGlobalRootCA.crt.pem" && \
    curl -sSL "$azure_cert_url" -o /tmp/azure-ca.crt && \
    keytool -import -alias azure-digicert -file /tmp/azure-ca.crt \
        -keystore /usr/lib/jvm/java-17-openjdk/lib/security/cacerts \
        -storepass changeit -noprompt && \
    rm /tmp/azure-ca.crt

RUN addgroup -g 1001 app && \
    adduser -D -u 1001 -G app app && \
    chown -R app:app /app

USER app

EXPOSE 3000

HEALTHCHECK --interval=30s --timeout=3s --start-period=5s --retries=3 \
    CMD curl -f http://localhost:3000/api/health || exit 1

CMD ["java", "-jar", "/app/app.jar"]
